# Permit.io Python SDK

Python SDK for interacting with the Permit.io full-stack permissions platform.

## Installation

```py
pip install permit
```

## Documentation

[Read the documentation at Permit.io website](https://docs.permit.io/sdk/python/quickstart-python)
